Overview
========

**distutils644** monkey-patches Python distutils_
to normalize metadata in generated tarballs:

- ownership (root:root),
- permissions (0644 or 0755),
- order of directory entries (sorted),
- tar format (ustar).

.. _distutils:
   https://docs.python.org/2/library/distutils.html

Usage
=====

Add this to ``setup.py``:

.. code:: python

   try:
       import distutils644
   except ImportError:
       pass
   else:
       distutils644.install()

Prerequisites
=============

* Python 2.7 or â‰¥ 3.2

